    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="918221453">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-918221453" class="vote-count">5</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-918221453" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="918221453">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1385284/">鲁人鲁话</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-05-02</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">第一章《祸起萧墙》，郑伯克段于鄢。第二章《五侯争霸》。第三章《南方崛起》，楚、吴、越的崛起。第四章《礼崩乐坏》，卿大夫夺权，如三家分晋，田陈代齐。第五章《商鞅变法》。第六章《合纵连横》，讲苏秦张仪冯驩吕不韦。叙述流畅，新意不多，可作扫盲之用。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

