  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6480601/" class="title-link">历史不是一场赌博</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6480601"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/67430757/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/67430757/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">jimmy</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-27"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-27 14:37:09</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6480601_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         算是一本有一定可读性的历史普及书，但在高度、广度、宽度上乏善可陈。        不认同易中天把一些历史的选择归结为“赌博”，比如，他在说郑庄公放纵叔段时说这是郑庄公的“一场豪赌”，第一赌叔段和武姜必反；第二赌他们谋反必败。还有后面把吕不韦也说成了“赌博”。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6480601/#comments">(4回应)</a>
